            "column_name": "Group",
            "description": [
              "Also known as a cohort. This is the specific kind of VIP client associated with a CID. There are four: Investor (those who had an account equity greater than 2.5 million USD the month before), Top50 (those who were in the top 50 for volume or commission the month before), ClosedTrader (a group of hand selected traders), and Friend (a group of hand selected clients). Each client / CID gets only one group, and cannot be assigned to another."
